column2: select m.*, o.objid, o.photoExtractID, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 , o.fuv_mag, o.fuv_magerr, o.fuv_artifact, o.nuv_mag, o.nuv_magerr, o.nuv_artifact into mydb.neigh_galex_tmp from MyDB.initial as m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN photoobjall as o ON n.objid = o.objid
